


<!-- @namespace    sugar.js.string -->

# ```js parse ```


Parse a string and convert it into his native data type like date, number, boolean, etc...

## Parameters

- **value**  String: The value to convert



## Example (js)

```js
import parse from '@coffeekraken/sugar/js/string/parse';
parse('10'); // => 10
```
